profile.name: Ahmed BENTABET
profile.about:
I specialize in building high-performance, secure backend systems with a focus on optimization and efficiency. With hands-on experience in Python, C, SQL, and low-level programming, I tackle complex technical challenges head-on to deliver robust solutions.

At ALX Africa, I worked on real-world projects that sharpened my skills in performance tuning, security, and system architecture. These experiences have given me a deep understanding of backend development, from optimizing code to securing large-scale applications.

I approach every project with a focus on solving problems through clean, efficient code. My goal is to collaborate on projects where I can apply my expertise in backend systems and continue to grow as a developer.

If you have an interesting project in mind, feel free to contact me at contact.bentabet@gmail.com or on Telegram: @ahmedbentabet.
